        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You recognize the dreaded illumantula from databases the Starfinder Society discovered in Eternity and know without a doubt the danger it—and the First Ones—pose to the Pact Worlds. While you know you can't defeat such a formidable creation yourself (and you hope you'll never have to try!), you've trained to combat robots and other technological creatures the First Ones are known to have created.</p>\n<p>Choose two attribute boosts. One must be to <strong>Strength</strong> or <strong>Dexterity</strong>, and one is a free attribute boost.</p>\n<p>You're trained in your choice of either the Computers or Crafting skill, as well as the Robot Lore skill. You gain a skill feat: @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.feats.Item.Phreaker]{Phreaker} if you chose Computers or @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.feats.Item.Quick Repair] if you chose Crafting.</p>"
